{{Top|leg}}
A '''remote slicer''' was an illegal device which could copy a [[Starship/Legends|starship's]] memory banks&mdash;either everything or only select parts&mdash;remotely. The ''[[Rock Dragon]]'' and ''[[Slave IV]]'' had these pieces of equipment on board. Data that could be obtained in this fashion included [[Astrogation/Legends|star charts]], the coordinates of recently visited [[Planet/Legends|planets]], and other data kept within a vessel's main [[Computer/Legends|computer]].

==Appearances==
*''[[Young Jedi Knights: Shards of Alderaan]]'' {{1st}}
*''[[Young Jedi Knights: The Emperor's Plague]]''

